name: TurboTax 2012 State Tax Form
summary: Learn about .TT2012STATE files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: State tax forms are not included with TurboTax. Instead, they are automatically downloaded when you begin a specific state return. A free state return is included with TurboTax Deluxe, Premier, and Home & Business editions.

description: State tax form used by TurboTax, a program used for completing United States tax returns; contains a tax form for an individual state and is used when filing a state tax return.
